snippet.title: Ruthless Conquest
snippet.description:
Download for iOS: https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/ruthless-conquest/id1449785021?ls=1&mt=8
Download for Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.candyrufusgames.ruthlessconquest
Download installer for Windows: https://www.dropbox.com/s/1ry7ydmr6aj3m09/SetupRuthlessConquest-1.1.1.exe?dl=1
Download for Amazon devices: https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B07M5QSVS3

No ads, no in-app purchases, completely free. Enjoy!

This game is a 2018 Christmas gift for Survivalcraft community. Local and internet multiplayer available. Start an internet game, wait for people to join and play.

More info at kaalus.wordpress.com.
